" data-text=\"Ἴσιδι\"><span data-text=\"Ἴσιδι\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"\">.....]</span></span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Θεόδωρος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Θεόδωρος\"><span data-text=\"Θεόδωρος\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"\">ΘΕΟΔΩΡΟ[.</span></span></span><span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;M[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div>"
